"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-samson-dauda-flexes-his-way-to-2024-mr-olympia-title-pictures-video-watch-result\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9373552194808472, \"rank\": 0.06435313785984732, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbSamson Dauda flexes his way to 2024 Mr Olympia title - PICTURES  Samson Dauda won the 2024 Mr Olympia contest at Resorts World Theater in Las Vegas, scooping the richest prize in the sport.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9373552194808472, \"rank\": 0.06435313785984732, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 184, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9493844517268114e-25, \"text\": \"Samson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\"}, {\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.321013511827857e-13, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9493844517268114e-25, \"text\": \"Samson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.321013511827857e-13, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}, {\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"score\": 0.6864910409867201, \"rank\": 0.45665445316049896, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samson Daudawon the2024 Mr Olympiacontest on Saturday night at Resorts World Theater in Las Vegas.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9493844517268114e-25, \"text\": \"Samson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samson\"}, {\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"score\": 0.6864910409867201, \"rank\": 0.45665445316049896, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born on11 March 1992in Nigeria to parents Patrick and Helen Dauda, he later moved to the United Kingdom and now resides in the United States.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 498, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9576696419682555, \"rank\": 0.044200950128841475, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danica_Patrick\", \"score\": 0.997126393561204, \"rank\": 0.002510367422341685, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danica_Patrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danica_Patrick\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9699387543404726, \"rank\": 0.030992924504863698, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999983092457765, \"rank\": 1.511280034756256e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dauda won his first Olympia title - and the richest prize in the sport's history.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.321013511827857e-13, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It came at the end of a tense competition that saw the judges perform several callouts before finally feeling confident in their decision to announce a new champion.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dauda completed a long, arduous journey to the pinnacle of bodybuilding on Saturday, winning the Mr Olympia competition and beating out two former champions, Iran'sHadi Choopanand AmericanDerek Lunsford, to collect the title.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dauda's victory ensured that the Mr Olympia title would return to the United Kingdom for the first time since Dorian Yates's six-year run atop the industry ended in 1997.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9699387543404726, \"rank\": 0.030992924504863698, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dorian_Yates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dorian Yates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15982795\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dorian_Yates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dorian_Yates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dauda won $600 000 (R10.5 million), a record payout for a Mr Olympia winner.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Choopan was awarded $250 000 (R4.37 million).\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The moment he was announced as the victor, Dauda dropped to his knees and broke down in tears before he hoisted the most coveted prize in his sport.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saturday's results marked the second year in a row that 2022 champion Choopan finished in second place.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It also meant that the 2023 champion, Lunsford, fell to third place this year.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dauda was not only the judge's choice for the win but also was named thePeople's Champion.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He received a championship belt and trophy.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After several callouts and great uncertainty as to which competitor would ultimately impress the judges enough to earn their selection as the winner, Dauda emerged victoriously, announcing his arrival at the peak of the bodybuilding world with a win on its grandest stage.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Chris (@_capturedbychris_)  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999740014742194, \"rank\": 2.563413340136508e-05, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.6777716645110899, \"rank\": 0.4754206541250586, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2409, \"end\": 2417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9806189803707077, \"rank\": 0.0